{"pageProps":{"note":{"id":"vn4QH8axQkezeOvv8cSG5","title":"ZigBee Home Automation","desc":"","updated":1656828840355,"created":1645185550463,"custom":{},"fname":"proj.zb-home-automation","type":"note","vault":{"fsPath":"vault"},"contentHash":"71b23e474f90f06b22a4a3bbd65ee863","links":[{"type":"wiki","from":{"fname":"proj.zb-home-automation","id":"vn4QH8axQkezeOvv8cSG5","vaultName":"vault"},"value":"ee.nrf52840.dongle","alias":"ee.nrf52840.dongle","position":{"start":{"line":4,"column":3,"offset":13},"end":{"line":4,"column":25,"offset":35},"indent":[]},"xvault":false,"sameFile":false,"to":{"fname":"ee.nrf52840.dongle"}},{"type":"wiki","from":{"fname":"proj.zb-home-automation","id":"vn4QH8axQkezeOvv8cSG5","vaultName":"vault"},"value":"ee.nrf-connect-sdk","alias":"ee.nrf-connect-sdk","position":{"start":{"line":5,"column":3,"offset":38},"end":{"line":5,"column":25,"offset":60},"indent":[]},"xvault":false,"sameFile":false,"to":{"fname":"ee.nrf-connect-sdk"}},{"type":"wiki","from":{"fname":"proj.zb-home-automation","id":"vn4QH8axQkezeOvv8cSG5","vaultName":"vault"},"value":"ee.ha","alias":"ee.ha","position":{"start":{"line":9,"column":40,"offset":109},"end":{"line":9,"column":49,"offset":118},"indent":[]},"xvault":false,"sameFile":false,"to":{"fname":"ee.ha"}},{"type":"wiki","from":{"fname":"proj.zb-home-automation","id":"vn4QH8axQkezeOvv8cSG5","vaultName":"vault"},"value":"ee.zb","alias":"ee.zb","position":{"start":{"line":9,"column":56,"offset":125},"end":{"line":9,"column":65,"offset":134},"indent":[]},"xvault":false,"sameFile":false,"to":{"fname":"ee.zb"}},{"type":"wiki","from":{"fname":"proj.zb-home-automation","id":"vn4QH8axQkezeOvv8cSG5","vaultName":"vault"},"value":"ee.zb.coordinator","alias":"ee.zb.coordinator","position":{"start":{"line":13,"column":30,"offset":254},"end":{"line":13,"column":51,"offset":275},"indent":[]},"xvault":false,"sameFile":false,"to":{"fname":"ee.zb.coordinator"}},{"type":"wiki","from":{"fname":"proj.zb-home-automation","id":"vn4QH8axQk